      <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        Different aspect ratios for various video formats and layout needs.
      </p>

      <Card>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 p-6">
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h3
              class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-center"
            >
              9:16 (Portrait)
            </h3>
            <TikTokEmbed
